OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDaniel Morgan: Met Police  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fapproach to tackling       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcorruption is flawed,      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Metropolitan Police's approach to  
OL,6, tackling corruption within its ranks is
OL,7, "fundamentally flawed", an inspection  
OL,8, by the police watchdog has concluded.  
OL,10,FThe watchdog found the force had       
OL,11,Frecruited people with criminal         
OL,12,Fconnections in the last two years, and 
OL,13,Fmore than 100 staff had broken the law.
OL,15,FThe Met welcomed the report and said it
OL,16,Fwas committed to tackling corruption.  
OL,18,FIt follows the failed investigation    
OL,19,Finto the 1987 murder of private        
OL,20,Finvestigator Daniel Morgan.            
